item.title: 3d Printed WCR Magnets
item.description: In 2022 I got my Level 2 Wheel chair rugby coach qualification after nearly 4 years in the sport. To help coach a diverse team of people some with cognitive impairments having clear visuals of chair to chair and chair to court helps communicate tactics and session activities.
